<note lang="eng">cf. <xref doc="t.6.1.21" from="t.6.1.21.c14">6.1.21.c14</xref></note>
The <foreign lang="sux">um</foreign> bird flees, running away from its own behind.</p></lg>
<lg id="t.6.1.19.d4" type="proverb" n="19.d4"><p id="t6119.p21" n="6" corresp="c6119.D.19.d4.6">
<note lang="eng">cf. <xref doc="t.6.1.02" from="t.6.1.02.c12">6.1.02.c12</xref></note>
Like an <foreign lang="sux">um</foreign> bird &X;&X;.</p></lg>
<lg id="t.6.1.19.d5" type="proverb" n="19.d5"><p id="t6119.p22" n="7" corresp="c6119.D.19.d5.7">
<note lang="eng">cf. <xref doc="t.6.2.5">6.2.5: IM 62823 Seg. B l. 3</xref></note>
