</lg></div1><div1 type="segment" n="G">
<lg id="t.6.1.19.g1" type="proverb" n="19.g1"><p id="t6119.p40" n="1" corresp="c6119.G.19.g1.1">
<note lang="eng">cf. <xref doc="t.6.1.03" from="t.6.1.03.117">6.1.03.117</xref></note>
You should lift it all together, but put it down in pieces.</p></lg>
<lg id="t.6.1.19.g2" type="proverb" n="19.g2"><p id="t6119.p41" n="2-4" corresp="c6119.G.19.g2.2">
